title: idontwannabeyouanymore
author: Billie Eilish
lyrics:
[00:17.03] Don't be that way, fall apart twice a day
[00:25.03] I just wish you could feel what you say
[00:34.08] Show, never tell, but I know you too well
[00:41.86] Kinda mood that you wish you could sell
[00:50.82] If teardrops could be bottled, there'd be swimming pools filled by models
[00:58.97] Told, "A tight dress is what makes you a whore"
[01:07.43] If "I love you" was a promise, would you break it, if you're honest?
[01:15.96] Tell the mirror what you know she's heard before
[01:17.15] 
[01:25.30] I don't wanna be you anymore
[01:27.79] 
[01:42.17] Hands getting cold, losing feeling is getting old
[01:49.93] Was I made from a broken mold?
[01:58.86] Hurt, I can't shake, we've made every mistake
[02:06.96] Only you know the way that I break
[02:15.71] If teardrops could be bottled, there'd be swimming pools filled by models
[02:23.99] Told, "A tight dress is what makes you a whore"
[02:32.53] If "I love you" was a promise, would you break it, if you're honest?
[02:40.82] Tell the mirror what you know she's heard before
[02:49.27] I, I don't wanna be you
[02:58.42] I don't wanna be you
[03:06.93] I don't wanna be you anymore
[03:17.84]
